blabel (1.00-a13) buster; urgency=medium

  * Printer name sanity check in blabel-print.pl.
  * Implemented quiet mode in blabel-print.pl.
  * blabel-print.pl is now feature complete!
  * blabel-print.pl's graphical engine is partitially rewritten, hopefully
    the issue with missing or extra black lines is finally dealt with.
  * Autocut is now controllable from GUI.

